If you want to use a different Google account,
use the Google Play Games app to switch.

Label for a button used to generate an account-linking code (which can be entered on another account to link the two together)
Description for account-linking, which lets you share progress and inventory between multiple accounts (on different platforms, etc.)

english value:
To link two accounts, generate a code on the first
and enter that code on the second.  Data from the
second account will then be shared between both.
(Data from the first account will be lost)

You can link up to ${COUNT} accounts.

IMPORTANT: only link accounts that you own;
If you link with friends’ accounts you will not
be able to play online at the same time.
translated value:
Yhdistääksesi kaksi käyttäjää, luo koodi ensimmäisellä käyttäjällä ja kirjoita tuo koodi toisella käyttäjällä. Data toiselta käyttäjältä jaetaan molempien välillä. (Data ensimmäiseltä käyttäjältä katoaa)

Pystyt yhdistämään ${COUNT} käyttäjää.

TÄRKEÄÄ: yhdistä vain käyttäjiä jotka omistat; Jos yhdistät käyttäjäsi kaverisi käyttäjän kanssa, et pysty pelaamaan netissä samaan aikaan.

description: Name for an option to link two accounts together, sharing progress and inventory between them.

Switch off the power on the back of your PS3, make sure
Bluetooth is enabled on your Mac, then connect your controller
to your Mac via a USB cable to pair the two. From then on, you
can use the controller's home button to connect it to your Mac
in either wired (USB) or wireless (Bluetooth) mode.

On some Macs you may be prompted for a passcode when pairing.
If this happens, see the following tutorial or google for help.




PS3 controllers connected wirelessly should show up in the device
list in System Preferences->Bluetooth. You may need to remove them
from that list when you want to use them with your PS3 again.

Also make sure to disconnect them from Bluetooth when not in
use or their batteries will continue to drain.

Bluetooth should handle up to 7 connected devices,
though your mileage may vary.

To use a PS3 controller with your OUYA, simply connect it with a USB cable
once to pair it.  Doing this may disconnect your other controllers, so
you should then restart your OUYA and unplug the USB cable.

From then on you should be able to use the controller's HOME button to
connect it wirelessly. When you are done playing, hold the HOME button
for 10 seconds to turn the controller off; otherwise it may remain on
and waste batteries.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "Don't run all the time.  Really.  You will fall off cliffs."]
english value: Don't run all the time.  Really.  You will fall off cliffs.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "Don't spin for too long; you'll become dizzy and fall."]
description: Tip for a new "dizzy" feature being added soon to prevent players from just spinning constantly
english value: Don't spin for too long; you'll become dizzy and fall.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Hold any button to run.  (Trigger buttons work well if you have them)']
english value: Hold any button to run.  (Trigger buttons work well if you have them)

key: ['translations', 'tips', "Hold down any button to run. You'll get places faster\nbut won't turn very well, so watch out for cliffs."]
english value:
Hold down any button to run. You'll get places faster
but won't turn very well, so watch out for cliffs.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Ice bombs are not very powerful, but they freeze\nwhoever they hit, leaving them vulnerable to shattering.']
english value:
Ice bombs are not very powerful, but they freeze
whoever they hit, leaving them vulnerable to shattering.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "If someone picks you up, punch them and they'll let go.\nThis works in real life too."]
english value:
If someone picks you up, punch them and they'll let go.
This works in real life too.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "If you are short on controllers, install the '${REMOTE_APP_NAME}' app\non your mobile devices to use them as controllers."]
english value:
If you are short on controllers, install the '${REMOTE_APP_NAME}' app
on your mobile devices to use them as controllers.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'If you get a sticky-bomb stuck to you, jump around and spin in circles. You might\nshake the bomb off, or if nothing else your last moments will be entertaining.']
english value:
If you get a sticky-bomb stuck to you, jump around and spin in circles. You might
shake the bomb off, or if nothing else your last moments will be entertaining.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'If you kill an enemy in one hit you get double points for it.']
english value: If you kill an enemy in one hit you get double points for it.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'If you pick up a curse, your only hope for survival is to\nfind a health powerup in the next few seconds.']
english value:
If you pick up a curse, your only hope for survival is to
find a health powerup in the next few seconds.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "If you stay in one place, you're toast. Run and dodge to survive.."]
english value: If you stay in one place, you're toast. Run and dodge to survive..

key: ['translations', 'tips', "If you've got lots of players coming and going, turn on 'auto-kick-idle-players'\nunder settings in case anyone forgets to leave the game."]
english value:
If you've got lots of players coming and going, turn on 'auto-kick-idle-players'
under settings in case anyone forgets to leave the game.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'If your device gets too warm or you\'d like to conserve battery power,\nturn down "Visuals" or "Resolution" in Settings->Graphics']
english value:
If your device gets too warm or you'd like to conserve battery power,
turn down "Visuals" or "Resolution" in Settings->Graphics

key: ['translations', 'tips', "If your framerate is choppy, try turning down resolution\nor visuals in the game's graphics settings."]
english value:
If your framerate is choppy, try turning down resolution
or visuals in the game's graphics settings.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'In Capture-the-Flag, your own flag must be at your base to score, If the other\nteam is about to score, stealing their flag can be a good way to stop them.']
english value:
In Capture-the-Flag, your own flag must be at your base to score, If the other
team is about to score, stealing their flag can be a good way to stop them.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "In hockey, you'll maintain more speed if you turn gradually."]
english value: In hockey, you'll maintain more speed if you turn gradually.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "It's easier to win with a friend or two helping."]
english value: It's easier to win with a friend or two helping.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "Jump just as you're throwing to get bombs up to the highest levels."]
english value: Jump just as you're throwing to get bombs up to the highest levels.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Land-mines are a good way to stop speedy enemies.']
english value: Land-mines are a good way to stop speedy enemies.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Many things can be picked up and thrown, including other players.  Tossing\nyour enemies off cliffs can be an effective and emotionally fulfilling strategy.']
english value:
Many things can be picked up and thrown, including other players.  Tossing
your enemies off cliffs can be an effective and emotionally fulfilling strategy.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "No, you can't get up on the ledge. You have to throw bombs."]
english value: No, you can't get up on the ledge. You have to throw bombs.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Players can join and leave in the middle of most games,\nand you can also plug and unplug controllers on the fly.']
english value:
Players can join and leave in the middle of most games,
and you can also plug and unplug controllers on the fly.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Practice using your momentum to throw bombs more accurately.']
english value: Practice using your momentum to throw bombs more accurately.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Punches do more damage the faster your fists are moving,\nso try running, jumping, and spinning like crazy.']
english value:
Punches do more damage the faster your fists are moving,
so try running, jumping, and spinning like crazy.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "Run back and forth before throwing a bomb\nto 'whiplash' it and throw it farther."]
english value:
Run back and forth before throwing a bomb
to 'whiplash' it and throw it farther.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Take out a group of enemies by\nsetting off a bomb near a TNT box.']
english value:
Take out a group of enemies by
setting off a bomb near a TNT box.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'The head is the most vulnerable area, so a sticky-bomb\nto the noggin usually means game-over.']
english value:
The head is the most vulnerable area, so a sticky-bomb
to the noggin usually means game-over.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'This level never ends, but a high score here\nwill earn you eternal respect throughout the world.']
english value:
This level never ends, but a high score here
will earn you eternal respect throughout the world.

key: ['translations', 'tips', "Throw strength is based on the direction you are holding.\nTo toss something gently in front of you, don't hold any direction."]
english value:
Throw strength is based on the direction you are holding.
To toss something gently in front of you, don't hold any direction.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Tired of the soundtrack?  Replace it with your own!\nSee Settings->Audio->Soundtrack']
english value:
Tired of the soundtrack?  Replace it with your own!
See Settings->Audio->Soundtrack

key: ['translations', 'tips', "Try 'Cooking off' bombs for a second or two before throwing them."]
english value: Try 'Cooking off' bombs for a second or two before throwing them.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Try tricking enemies into killing eachother or running off cliffs.']
english value: Try tricking enemies into killing eachother or running off cliffs.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Use the pick-up button to grab the flag < ${PICKUP} >']
english value: Use the pick-up button to grab the flag < ${PICKUP} >

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Whip back and forth to get more distance on your throws..']
english value: Whip back and forth to get more distance on your throws..

key: ['translations', 'tips', "You can 'aim' your punches by spinning left or right.\nThis is useful for knocking bad guys off edges or scoring in hockey."]
english value:
You can 'aim' your punches by spinning left or right.
This is useful for knocking bad guys off edges or scoring in hockey.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'You can judge when a bomb is going to explode based on the\ncolor of sparks from its fuse:  yellow..orange..red..BOOM.']
english value:
You can judge when a bomb is going to explode based on the
color of sparks from its fuse:  yellow..orange..red..BOOM.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'You can throw bombs higher if you jump just before throwing.']
english value: You can throw bombs higher if you jump just before throwing.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'You take damage when you whack your head on things,\nso try to not whack your head on things.']
english value:
You take damage when you whack your head on things,
so try to not whack your head on things.

key: ['translations', 'tips', 'Your punches do much more damage if you are running or spinning.']
english value: Your punches do much more damage if you are running or spinning.
